sourcesContent: import houseCardImg from "../media/houseCard.png"; import { Box, Button, Container, Grid, Typography, styled } from "@mui/material"; import DisplayIcon from "../media/viewMore.png"; import NewImage1 from "../media/news.png.png"; import NewImage2 from "../media/news2.png.png"; import NewImage3 from "../media/news3.png.png"; import HeartIcon from '../media/Vector.png' import CalendarTodayIcon from '@mui/icons-material/CalendarToday'; import AccessTimeIcon from '@mui/icons-material/AccessTime'; import CommentIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Comment'; import AvatarIcon from '../media/avatar.png.png' const CustomBox = styled(Box)(({ theme }) => ({ bottom: 0, left: 0, backgroundColor: "white", padding: "20px", borderRadius: "10px", boxShadow: "0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)", [theme.breakpoints.down("md")]: { width: "100%", }, height: "200px", top: "80%", })); export default function MoreDetail() { return ( News, Tips & Guides Favorite destinations based on customer reviews Cultural 18 Sep 2024 6 mins 38 comments Ultimate Travel Planning Guide: 10 Tips for a Seamless Journey Jimmy Dave Keep Reading Top Rated California Sunset/Twilight Boat Cruise {/* */} 2 days 3 nights {/* */} 4-6 guests $48.25 / person Book Now Top Rated California Sunset/Twilight Boat Cruise {/* */} 2 days 3 nights {/* */} 4-6 guests $48.25 / person Book Now ); }
